  "body": "Estimated end-of-life date, accurate to within three months: 06-2027\r\nSee [the support level definitions](https://docs.datadoghq.com/tracing/trace_collection/compatibility/python/#releases) for more information.\r\n\r\n⚠️ An issue was detected with Profiling in this release, see #17378\r\n\r\n### Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- tracing: This fix resolves an issue where client side stats tags were not properly set.\r\n\r\n<!-- -->\r\n\r\n- internal: Fix a potential internal thread leak in fork-heavy applications.\r\n\r\n<!-- -->\r\n\r\n- internal: A crash that could occur post-fork in fork-heavy applications has been fixed."
